column1: Labour Force Status by Sex: Seasonally Adjusted (Qrtly-Mar/Jun/Sep/Dec)
HLFQ.S1F3S: Magnitude = Units, Unit = Percent, Description = Unemployment Rate - Total Both Sexes
All previously published figures are subject to revision when the seasonal adjustment program is run each quarter.
Labour force participation rate is the total labour force expressed as a percentage of the working-age population.
